00:29:24.990 --> 00:29:26.000
equal to each other.

00:29:26.000 --> 00:29:30.070
Because we know that's true.

00:29:30.070 --> 00:29:37.570
So mu A, in the gas phase,
temperature and with a partial

00:29:37.570 --> 00:29:45.350
pressure p sub A. Is equal to
