00:30:04.130 --> 00:30:05.600
what happens.

00:30:05.600 --> 00:30:07.246
So let's take the derivative
of this with

00:30:07.246 --> 00:30:08.220
respect to total pressure.

00:30:08.220 --> 00:30:09.860
Well, this isn't
