00:30:24.630 --> 00:30:32.500
So on this side here, we
have d mu A / dpA.

00:30:32.500 --> 00:30:40.840
So I'm taking d/dp
of both sides.

00:30:40.840 --> 00:30:42.980
Then by chain rule, dpA/dP.

00:30:48.250 --> 00:30:49.660
Constant temperature.

00:30:49.660 --> 00:30:56.690
And then on the right-hand
side, I have d mu A / dP,

00:30:56.690 --> 00:31:00.210
constant temperature.

00:31:00.210 --> 00:31:05.930
Well, d mu / dP, that may or may
