00:32:12.980 --> 00:32:15.490
And we've got these d
mu A / dpA, we've

00:32:15.490 --> 00:32:17.310
got d mu A / dP here.

00:32:17.310 --> 00:32:22.160
That's just the molar
volume of the gas.

00:32:22.160 --> 00:32:24.790
Right, because this is mu
